    <title>hexo themes: minos</title>
    <link href="https://mjc-alex.github.io/2023/05/22/hexo-themes-minos/"/>
    <id>https://mjc-alex.github.io/2023/05/22/hexo-themes-minos/</id>
    <published>2023-05-22T15:32:41.000Z</published>
    <updated>2023-05-22T15:51:46.529Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<html><head></head><body><h2 id="about-hexo"><a href="#about-hexo" class="headerlink" title="about hexo"></a>about hexo</h2><p>21.5.23, 我建立了我的第一个（正式的）博客，用的是Github + Hexo. 开头很顺利，今天换主题的时候有些小bug。在此记录过程，方便以后迁移。</p><ul><li><code>install node.js, git, hexo</code></li></ul><figure class="highlight bash hljs"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ npm i hexo-cli -g</span><br><span class="line">$ hexo -v <span class="hljs-comment"># to check for successful installation</span></span><br><span class="line">$ hexo init &lt;<span class="hljs-built_in">dir</span> name&gt;</span><br><span class="line">$ npm install ...</span><br><span class="line">$ hexo g <span class="hljs-comment"># generate static web page</span></span><br><span class="line">$ hexo s <span class="hljs-comment"># start local serve to preview, ctrl + click the url to open it</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><ul><li><code>connect your github</code><figure class="highlight bash hljs"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git config --global user.name <span class="hljs-string">"zz2summer"</span> </span><br><span class="line">git config --global user.email <span class="hljs-string">"xxxxx@163.com"</span></span><br><span class="line">ssh-keygen -t rsa -C <span class="hljs-string">"summer2zz@163.com"</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>  open github, click settings &gt; SSH and GPG keys, create a new ssh key.<figure class="highlight bash hljs"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="hljs-built_in">cat</span> ~/.ssh/id_rsa.pub</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>  copy the output to the new ssh key.</li><li><code>modify blog/_config.yml</code><br>  open _config.yml, change the last line:</li></ul><figure class="highlight bash hljs"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">deploy:</span><br><span class="line"><span class="hljs-built_in">type</span>: git</span><br><span class="line">repository: git@...</span><br><span class="line">branch: main</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure></body></html>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
    <summary type="html">&lt;html&gt;&lt;head&gt;&lt;/head&gt;&lt;body&gt;&lt;h2 id=&quot;about-hexo&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#about-hexo&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;about hexo&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;about hexo&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;21.5.23, 我建立了</summary>
      
    
    
    
    
